      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ON MACI (6) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten half a length (19.18) behind No Iron Team at Healesville. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and five minor placings from six starts. Overdue and expected to feature again. LAKEVIEW LIAM (2) finished seventh last time but the start prior broke the clock when winning over 435m at this track, taking a Mix 3/4 in a head turning 24.35. Expected to feature on best figures. FURIOUS FALCON (4) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (22.86) in a Grade 4/5 at Warragul last time out. Can hit the frame this time. CHAMPAGNE CUDDLE (3) has a solid strike rate at this distance.",
